#. Short description.
#, gp-priority: high
msgid ""
"Fast, accessible faceted product filtering for WooCommerce: AJAX filters, a "
"mobile drawer, and Core Web Vitals by design."
msgstr ""
"Filtrado facetado de productos rápido y accesible para WooCommerce: filtros "
"AJAX, un panel deslizante móvil y Core Web Vitals por diseño."

#. Plugin name.
#, gp-priority: high
msgid "Sieve - Faceted Filter for WooCommerce"
msgstr "Sieve - Filtro facetado para WooCommerce"

